[Episode 17]

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:40.710
Save William too?

00:01:45.690 --> 00:01:46.810
You promised him?

00:01:56.300 --> 00:02:00.290
[Stanley Prison]

00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:02.810
10,000 Pounds.

00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:07.400
You really have 10,000 Pounds in HSBC?

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:10.820
It was handled by Qiao Renyu.

00:02:10.850 --> 00:02:13.840
But I lost my deposit certificates.
Now, to withdraw the money,

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:15.580
I have to ask him. Understand?

00:02:16.380 --> 00:02:16.990
But...

00:02:17.540 --> 00:02:20.020
He's a death row prisoner
of the Gendarmerie Army.

00:02:20.020 --> 00:02:22.970
Heavily guarded.
No one is allowed to contact him.

00:02:22.970 --> 00:02:24.079
Do you understand?

00:02:24.579 --> 00:02:26.650
Mr. Fujii, please, please. Just... Just...

00:02:26.650 --> 00:02:27.810
Don't touch me!

00:02:27.810 --> 00:02:30.210
It's gonna take one minute. One minute!

00:02:30.210 --> 00:02:32.079
And... when I get the money...

00:02:32.079 --> 00:02:33.760
Sixty-forty.

00:02:33.790 --> 00:02:35.030
Sixty-forty.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.000
How does it sound?

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:42.740
In the past week,

00:02:42.740 --> 00:02:44.750
Macau's businesses have nearly collapsed.

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:48.079
Citizens can't even secure
rice or vegetables.

00:02:48.340 --> 00:02:49.930
The Portuguese Macau government

00:02:49.930 --> 00:02:52.890
probably won't last more than a month.

00:02:52.930 --> 00:02:56.329
The Empire's military currency
will inevitably be adopted.

00:02:56.930 --> 00:02:58.240
Well done.

00:02:59.150 --> 00:02:59.690
General,

00:03:00.580 --> 00:03:03.980
there are no urgent matters in Macau now.

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.330
If you have no other instructions,

00:03:06.580 --> 00:03:08.020
I'd like to go to Stanley Prison

00:03:08.020 --> 00:03:11.210
to interrogate Qiao Renyu once more.

00:03:14.020 --> 00:03:17.870
Sawa, the HKD has been abolished.

00:03:18.870 --> 00:03:21.810
What's the point of keeping track

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.680
of leaked serial numbers?

00:03:23.930 --> 00:03:25.560
Why waste your time?

00:03:28.860 --> 00:03:29.579
General,

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:34.180
I don't care about
the leaked serial numbers.

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:37.860
I want to find Qiao Renyu's collaborators

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:41.370
and uncover
the anti-Japanese organizations in Macau.

00:03:41.900 --> 00:03:42.960
I see.

00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:46.090
Since you insist,

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:50.300
very well.
I'll authorize the interrogation.

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:53.340
Thank you.

00:03:59.090 --> 00:04:02.820
Qiao Renyu is locked in the innermost cell
of the death row section.

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:04.580
Security here is tight.

00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:06.740
Without my orders,

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:08.710
no one can possibly access him.

00:04:09.710 --> 00:04:10.710
This way, please.

00:04:17.390 --> 00:04:18.890
Why is this door open?

00:04:19.870 --> 00:04:20.620
Warden,

00:04:20.620 --> 00:04:22.360
well... Chief Guard Fujii said

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:24.020
he needed to go in for a moment.

00:04:34.070 --> 00:04:34.500
Hey!

00:04:34.540 --> 00:04:36.000
Fujii, what are you doing?

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:37.300
Bastard!

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:37.820
Yes!

00:04:38.330 --> 00:04:41.260
Don't you know the prisoners inside
are on death row?

00:04:42.630 --> 00:04:44.230
Why did you bring someone in?

00:04:46.420 --> 00:04:47.390
Well...

00:05:05.990 --> 00:05:07.220
Qiao Renyu...

00:05:08.630 --> 00:05:10.390
is in this cell?

00:05:11.210 --> 00:05:12.000
Yes.

00:05:42.450 --> 00:05:45.600
Why did you open this cell?

00:05:48.690 --> 00:05:49.450
Explain!

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:51.600
It wasn't me.

00:05:51.620 --> 00:05:53.250
It's none of my business.

00:05:55.930 --> 00:05:57.260
It was this Englishman.

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:59.150
He wanted to see Qiao Renyu.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:00.500
No, no, no.

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:03.050
It wasn't my fault! It wasn't my fault!

00:06:19.330 --> 00:06:22.240
[Prison, No Entry Without Permission]

00:06:24.260 --> 00:06:24.990
Listen to me.

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:25.950
It wasn't me.

00:06:25.950 --> 00:06:27.060
I was forced.

00:06:27.190 --> 00:06:29.240
Someone wants to rescue Qiao Renyu.

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:31.950
I'll confess everything.

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:38.450
No rush.

00:06:40.620 --> 00:06:42.420
Come back with me and we'll talk.

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:50.040
Two full trucks
of British De La Rue printing plates?

00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:51.630
That's right.

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:55.830
Well done.

00:06:56.330 --> 00:06:57.420
Excellent!

00:06:58.360 --> 00:07:02.420
Now Chongqing's Customs Gold Unit
is done for.

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.120
Sawa,

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:05.700
you...

00:07:06.300 --> 00:07:09.010
made a great contribution to the Empire.

00:07:09.010 --> 00:07:11.010
This is truly a great contribution!

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:16.370
Unfortunately, this William...

00:07:16.390 --> 00:07:18.850
doesn't know
where the printing plates are.

00:07:21.770 --> 00:07:23.830
Are you sure he was telling the truth?

00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:27.830
This Englishman is a coward.

00:07:28.010 --> 00:07:29.120
Before we even tortured him,

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:31.370
he betrayed even his own wife.

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:33.090
I don't think he was lying.

00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:34.690
In that case,

00:07:36.190 --> 00:07:39.050
the only one
who knows where the printing plates are

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:41.570
is Qiao Renyu.

00:07:42.090 --> 00:07:43.680
After learning this,

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.930
I interrogated the HSBC staff.

00:07:46.300 --> 00:07:47.830
According to them,

00:07:47.830 --> 00:07:49.930
after Qiao Renyu returned
to the bank that day

00:07:49.930 --> 00:07:51.420
and completed the task
of transferring the printing plates,

00:07:51.420 --> 00:07:54.120
he met with Mr. Grayburn of HSBC

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:55.920
and had a conversation with him.

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.480
That means

00:07:57.950 --> 00:08:02.060
Mr. Grayburn might also know about it.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:05.100
Judging from this operation
to rescue Qiao Renyu,

00:08:05.690 --> 00:08:06.860
the Allied Forces not only have

00:08:06.860 --> 00:08:09.010
a dedicated intelligence station in Macau,

00:08:09.010 --> 00:08:13.160
allowing them to learn about
the printing plates earlier than we did,

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:14.090
but have also

00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:15.890
formed close cooperation

00:08:15.890 --> 00:08:17.860
with the underground
anti-Japanese organizations.

00:08:17.860 --> 00:08:19.640
Looks like their strength
cannot be underestimated.

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:21.470
Tomorrow you will be in command.

00:08:22.010 --> 00:08:24.330
Use that British woman
as the breakthrough point,

00:08:24.330 --> 00:08:26.250
set up an ambush,

00:08:26.770 --> 00:08:29.480
and wipe out the Allied Forces'
intelligence station in Macau,

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:31.570
along with the Hong Kong

00:08:31.570 --> 00:08:33.669
anti-Japanese organizations
involved in the operation,

00:08:33.669 --> 00:08:36.289
in one go.

00:08:37.820 --> 00:08:38.429
Yes.

00:08:39.220 --> 00:08:40.080
Chief,

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:43.820
we've received
all the documents and photographs.

00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:45.150
Yes.

00:08:47.820 --> 00:08:48.480
Yes.

00:08:51.990 --> 00:08:53.010
[Name: Mary Jones]

00:08:53.010 --> 00:08:55.290
Track down leads on this foreign woman
immediately.

00:08:55.290 --> 00:08:56.120
Yes.

00:09:00.690 --> 00:09:01.580
Once Mary takes back

00:09:01.580 --> 00:09:03.750
the flowerpot outside the window
of the emergency room,

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:05.340
start the rescue operation immediately.

00:09:05.340 --> 00:09:06.540
Any other questions?

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:07.410
-No.
-No.

00:09:08.350 --> 00:09:08.880
Let's go.

00:09:14.370 --> 00:09:15.970
Go over the previous routes again

00:09:15.970 --> 00:09:16.990
in your head,

00:09:17.450 --> 00:09:18.620
both of them.

00:09:21.940 --> 00:09:23.790
Chang, you're with me.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:24.600
Mary,

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.820
you're the key to this operation.

00:09:27.250 --> 00:09:28.710
Do you need anything else?

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.450
Where's the gun we brought?

00:09:49.820 --> 00:09:53.440
Durian! Durian!

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:09.030
[Casualty Ward]

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:13.020
[Suspend Use]

00:10:19.910 --> 00:10:20.030
Hurry.

00:10:20.030 --> 00:10:20.410
[Suspend Use]

00:10:20.410 --> 00:10:22.240
This person suddenly fell ill.
Begin immediate resuscitation.

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:22.860
This way.

00:10:33.540 --> 00:10:34.550
[Casualty Ward]

00:10:41.180 --> 00:10:41.840
Don't move!

00:10:47.910 --> 00:10:48.780
Is it her?

00:10:54.420 --> 00:10:56.100
Report to the Colonel immediately.

00:10:56.100 --> 00:10:56.480
Yes.

00:11:08.750 --> 00:11:09.320
Colonel,

00:11:09.620 --> 00:11:11.350
the contact has been captured.

00:11:11.630 --> 00:11:12.500
Very good.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:15.790
Proceed as planned.

00:11:21.380 --> 00:11:22.090
Mary,

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:24.410
I've already told the Imperial Army
everything.

00:11:24.410 --> 00:11:25.370
They know about Qiao Renyu

00:11:25.370 --> 00:11:26.700
and the printing paper.

00:11:27.870 --> 00:11:29.270
Your mission has failed.

00:11:29.580 --> 00:11:30.410
This game is over.

00:11:30.410 --> 00:11:31.470
Do you understand?

00:11:31.580 --> 00:11:33.510
But the Imperial Army is merciful.

00:11:33.700 --> 00:11:36.100
They're giving you a chance
to redeem yourself.

00:11:36.100 --> 00:11:38.070
The only thing is to help them

00:11:38.270 --> 00:11:39.410
bring in your comrades.

00:11:39.410 --> 00:11:39.940
Alright?

00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:41.790
We can be together again.

00:11:41.790 --> 00:11:42.270
They'll...

00:11:42.270 --> 00:11:43.750
even set us free.

00:11:43.750 --> 00:11:44.440
Mary.

00:11:45.380 --> 00:11:47.100
This is our last chance.

00:11:47.770 --> 00:11:49.030
You must take it.

00:11:59.820 --> 00:12:00.650
She agreed.

00:12:01.750 --> 00:12:02.600
She agreed.

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:06.080
Good.

00:12:07.030 --> 00:12:07.830
Let me ask you.

00:12:08.360 --> 00:12:09.890
What's the contact signal?

00:12:13.130 --> 00:12:15.060
There's a flowerpot by the window.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:17.790
I just need to shake it 3 times

00:12:18.890 --> 00:12:20.750
and they'll come in to pick him up.

00:12:47.890 --> 00:12:48.940
You two,

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:51.420
control the corridor
and the main entrance.

00:12:51.710 --> 00:12:52.370
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:12:54.220 --> 00:12:54.750
You,

00:12:55.370 --> 00:12:57.030
come here and give the signal.

00:13:57.060 --> 00:13:57.920
Chang!

00:14:21.620 --> 00:14:24.090
Put the whole city under martial law.

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:26.790
Conduct house-to-house searches.

00:14:26.810 --> 00:14:29.370
Seal off the piers and all beaches.

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:31.940
Don't let anyone

00:14:32.640 --> 00:14:34.540
without a Hong Kong Citizen ID go.

00:14:42.860 --> 00:14:46.550
[Hechang Electronics]

00:14:48.420 --> 00:14:50.110
The planned route is no longer viable.

00:14:50.110 --> 00:14:52.110
We'll have to take the backup route.

00:14:53.170 --> 00:14:55.370
This is a ticket for a ship
owned by Lyun Coeng in Macau.

00:14:55.370 --> 00:14:57.640
Lyun Coeng holds a special transit permit
issued by the Japanese Army.

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:59.700
This is your only way out of Hong Kong.

00:15:08.530 --> 00:15:09.930
Are you absolutely sure?

00:15:10.770 --> 00:15:11.600
Mary is dead?

00:15:17.020 --> 00:15:18.530
I'm sure.

00:15:47.300 --> 00:15:48.960
Where are Mary and Yang Chang?

00:15:50.810 --> 00:15:51.600
Mary is...

00:16:38.620 --> 00:16:39.210
Xian.

00:16:40.310 --> 00:16:41.910
Let her have some time alone.

00:17:00.770 --> 00:17:01.720
Show me your ID.

00:17:01.810 --> 00:17:03.410
The pier is temporarily cordoned off.

00:17:03.410 --> 00:17:04.980
No one is allowed to leave.

00:17:04.980 --> 00:17:07.040
All personnel are to receive checks.

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:13.849
Go. Go.

00:17:21.400 --> 00:17:23.079
There is a tung oil ship

00:17:23.099 --> 00:17:24.720
that has been detained
at Tsim Sha Tsui Pier

00:17:24.720 --> 00:17:27.329
due to the sudden lockdown
imposed by the Japanese.

00:17:27.329 --> 00:17:29.330
Xian, why are you asking about this?

00:17:29.400 --> 00:17:30.300
Do you have a way

00:17:30.330 --> 00:17:31.540
to get this ship back?

00:17:32.210 --> 00:17:33.360
Well...

00:17:34.090 --> 00:17:35.550
The martial law order came from

00:17:35.550 --> 00:17:36.880
the Japanese Hong Kong Command.

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:37.830
I'm just a little clerk.

00:17:37.830 --> 00:17:38.380
I...

00:17:38.770 --> 00:17:40.090
don't have that kind of authority.

00:17:40.090 --> 00:17:41.160
Isn't Lyun Coeng

00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:42.070
directly under

00:17:42.070 --> 00:17:44.500
the Japanese
Southern China Expeditionary Army Command?

00:17:44.500 --> 00:17:46.530
That carries far more weight
than the Hong Kong Command.

00:17:46.530 --> 00:17:48.270
You're a shipping manager after all.

00:17:48.270 --> 00:17:49.380
If you put some thought into it,

00:17:49.380 --> 00:17:50.640
there must be a chance.

00:17:51.770 --> 00:17:52.720
To be honest,

00:17:52.970 --> 00:17:55.010
before you called me for this meeting,

00:17:55.010 --> 00:17:57.250
I had already planned
to resign from Lyun Coeng.

00:17:57.250 --> 00:17:58.660
I even wrote my resignation letter.

00:17:58.660 --> 00:17:59.880
You can't resign now.

00:18:05.790 --> 00:18:07.390
What exactly is on that ship?

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:09.750
You'd better not

00:18:09.750 --> 00:18:10.680
ask about that.

00:18:11.040 --> 00:18:13.380
Knowing too much
would only put you at risk.

00:18:13.380 --> 00:18:14.440
All I can say is that

00:18:14.730 --> 00:18:16.410
if there's even the slightest chance,

00:18:16.410 --> 00:18:18.510
you must
get that tung oil ship back to Macau,

00:18:18.510 --> 00:18:19.530
along with everyone on board,

00:18:19.530 --> 00:18:21.720
before the Japanese search begins.

00:18:23.160 --> 00:18:24.290
I'm counting on you.

00:18:25.940 --> 00:18:26.570
Alright.

00:18:27.380 --> 00:18:28.770
Xian, since you've asked,

00:18:28.770 --> 00:18:29.920
I'll do my best.

00:18:31.640 --> 00:18:32.240
Hongshen,

00:18:32.550 --> 00:18:33.290
thank you.

00:18:34.090 --> 00:18:34.850
Remember,

00:18:35.270 --> 00:18:36.280
we don't have much time.

00:18:36.280 --> 00:18:37.140
You must hurry.

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:38.610
I see.

00:18:39.660 --> 00:18:40.690
Mr. Huang,

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:41.900
we found it.

00:18:42.160 --> 00:18:42.980
That British woman

00:18:42.980 --> 00:18:44.980
is living in a shack in the slum area.

00:18:45.560 --> 00:18:46.850
Gather all our men.

00:18:46.900 --> 00:18:47.570
Let's go now.

00:18:47.570 --> 00:18:48.310
Yes!

00:18:49.040 --> 00:18:50.180
[Ruiai]

00:18:55.540 --> 00:18:56.270
Give it to me!

00:19:18.700 --> 00:19:19.630
She just left.

00:19:19.960 --> 00:19:20.770
Split up and chase her!

00:19:20.770 --> 00:19:21.460
Yes!

00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:22.030
Let's go!

00:19:29.340 --> 00:19:32.660
[Xihe]

00:19:42.310 --> 00:19:44.150
[Xiangdao Daily]

00:19:47.210 --> 00:19:48.010
Manager He,

00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:49.500
what is this?

00:19:49.940 --> 00:19:50.570
Chairman,

00:19:51.270 --> 00:19:53.900
you know about our tung oil ship
being detained in Hong Kong,

00:19:53.900 --> 00:19:55.110
don't you?

00:19:55.500 --> 00:19:56.700
Wasn't that because of
the temporary lockdown

00:19:56.700 --> 00:19:58.270
at the Hong Kong piers?

00:19:58.270 --> 00:20:00.350
The company is just cooperating with them.

00:20:00.350 --> 00:20:02.180
Why did that make you want to resign?

00:20:02.180 --> 00:20:03.880
With Lyun Coeng's special background,

00:20:03.880 --> 00:20:05.200
ordinary Chinese merchants

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:07.240
usually wouldn't do business with us.

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:09.460
The only reason
we could secure a few smugglers

00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:10.330
to supply us

00:20:10.530 --> 00:20:12.050
is that Lyun Coeng holds

00:20:12.050 --> 00:20:13.900
shipping privileges
from the Imperial Army.

00:20:13.900 --> 00:20:14.860
But this time,

00:20:14.890 --> 00:20:17.440
the company's tung oil ship
was actually detained in Hong Kong.

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:18.180
Those in the know

00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:20.070
understand that we're just cooperating
with the Imperial Army,

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:20.790
but those who don't

00:20:20.790 --> 00:20:21.500
might assume

00:20:21.500 --> 00:20:23.250
that Lyun Coeng has lost its privileges.

00:20:23.250 --> 00:20:24.750
These smugglers

00:20:24.750 --> 00:20:27.010
rely on protection.

00:20:27.140 --> 00:20:27.960
In this case,

00:20:27.960 --> 00:20:29.890
who would dare do business with us?

00:20:30.030 --> 00:20:30.240
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:20:30.240 --> 00:20:31.850
My phone
hasn't stopped ringing since earlier.

00:20:31.850 --> 00:20:34.220
Every deal I had lined up
has fallen through.

00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:35.880
I have no choice but to resign.

00:20:37.790 --> 00:20:40.350
I didn't expect
that a single ship getting detained

00:20:40.350 --> 00:20:42.710
would cause such a huge misunderstanding.

00:20:42.710 --> 00:20:43.660
I admit

00:20:43.690 --> 00:20:45.960
I was careless.

00:20:47.800 --> 00:20:48.310
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:20:48.310 --> 00:20:49.110
No.

00:20:49.980 --> 00:20:51.850
We must get the ship back immediately,

00:20:51.850 --> 00:20:54.030
and it must be
before any other ships are released,

00:20:54.030 --> 00:20:58.140
to show Lyun Coeng's
authority and privileges.

